### Wellness Service demo (via API Gateway)
###
### 1) Get an access token (see scripts/test-api.sh), then paste it below:
@token = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. GET all resources
GET http://localhost:8082/api/resources
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 2. Filter by category
GET http://localhost:8082/api/resources/category/mental-health
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 3. Search by keyword
GET http://localhost:8082/api/resources/search?keyword=Mindfulness
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 4. POST create a new resource (requires staff role)
POST http://localhost:8082/api/resources
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Mindfulness Basics",
  "description": "Intro guide to meditation",
  "category": "mental-health",
  "url": "https://example.com/mindfulness"
}
